item.title: Exit Strategy // Stickmanadventures [Feedback Needed]
item.dc:creator: iammane
item.description:
See I dunno, I think this is a great example of less is more. I think if this was all jammed up with more instruments it would be too much.

This is pretty sweet, it held my interest the whole time. I like what you’ve done with the drum work. Listening a second time…

It’s definitely got this video game style structure going on which isn’t normally my bag but it’s working for me on this one. I like the “strummed” chords, and the transition from the intro to the (we’ll call it B part) and back is really smooth.

Yeah I like it. Solid job!
